                                Encoder: SMiLE                             
                                                                            
   READNFO - First 2 minutes of the video are from the arabic release, it   
   is pretty poor quality but not a massive lot happens. People have been   
   saying that there are several minutes of video missing from previous     
   releases, when in fact thats just mainly the end credits. Ok now I       
   decided to go for INSPiRAL's release because they have once again done   
   a great job at cutting down the camera movement throughout the movie.    
   I did a lot of heavy filtering to this, the video had that "Tinge" -     
   (Bad IVTC) So I ran a select few filters to deal with the issue and      
   managed to tone down the tinge whilst not totally destroying the video.  
   Brightneed/Contrast, HSV and RGB were also tweaked throughout the        
   filtering process. I must warn you that the video is still very dark     
   and will still contain elements of the tinge in certain effected scenes  
   the audio is pretty basic CAM audio but at least it's avaliable. As      
   INSPiRAL said - These Underworld movies have never looked great as CAMs  
   Enjoy Folks! 
